Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:07.76,Vinland-picture,,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,960)\fad(460,500)}公元987年 休伦迦瓦格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.39,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,注：休伦迦瓦格海战，是挪威军队驱逐维京海盗的战争，发生在挪威西部沿岸海域。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么愣神了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:12.88,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 睡了一小会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:19.93,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,阵型拉得太开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这么下去我们会顶不住敌人的第二波攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.00,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托鲁克尔 等弗洛基靠近过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.73,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你就一口气把战线推过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:31.31,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那个骰子头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,也行吧 那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.31,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我来拖住敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:38.85,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,拖住敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你要怎么到那种地方去…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:47.02,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,身轻如燕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,等等 一个人就冲过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,玛利亚 对不起
Comment: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:38.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.48,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}To sink or swim、生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.48,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}为生存孤注一掷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.89,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}Dog eat dog world だと言い聞かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.89,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}提醒自己世界的残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.11,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.11,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}哪里出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:11.47,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}Survival of the fittest、弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:11.47,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}适者生存 弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.51,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}If it’s the world that our wisdom will lead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.51,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}如果智慧将引领世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.21,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}Well, tell me what went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.21,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}那么告诉我是哪里出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.06,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}I've paid my dues
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.06,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}我已历尽苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.16,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}I've sold my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.16,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}我已出卖灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.62,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}So tell me, what is left for me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.62,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}所以告诉我 当我放弃一切之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.24,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}when I've given up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.24,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}我还能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.47,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}ねぇ、どう描いてたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.47,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}呐 当初描绘的景色是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:39.25,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}どの景色を見ても 何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:39.25,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}不管面对什么景色 我都变得无动于衷
