Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.12,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}真実の見えない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.12,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}在这个看不见真相的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.72,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}善と悪のバランスを保ち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:14.72,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}维持着善与恶的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.08,Vinland-op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}殺すか殺されるかの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.08,Vinland-op-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}这是一个充斥杀戮的
