Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:25.61,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔芬 去给绵羊喂饲料和挤牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.60,Vinland-pronunciation,,0,0,0,,{\pos(985,1000)}    Markland
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,离开了马克兰之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:15.89,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,注：马克兰，意为“森林之地”，维京人抵达北美的据点之一，推测位于加拿大拉布拉多地区。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们的船进一步往南航行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,海风告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,前方有更丰饶的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:34.17,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然后我终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,新大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:49.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,硕果累累 绿草茵茵的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.68,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我给这片土地取了个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.49,Vinland-pronunciation,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,1000)}    Vinland
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,名叫「文兰」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.71,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,注：文兰，意为“草原之地”，维京人抵达北美的据点之一，\N现有考古遗迹证明在加拿大纽芬兰岛北端一带。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,对本大爷雷夫·埃里克森有点改观了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.67,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,注：据史诗记载，他是第一位发现美洲的欧洲探险家，比哥伦布早500年。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.98,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好厉害 雷夫大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:16.94,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然后呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:17.78,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那里有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那里暖和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,比冰岛还要大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,对啊 比这里暖和多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.83,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,草原一望无际
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们还遇到了原住民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.61,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,虽然语言不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是没多久我们就成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:43.52,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这些羽饰和这根烟杆就是他们送的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,听好了 这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.88,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有真正的战士才能佩戴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:55.18,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,你看 很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.96,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来孩子们还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.77,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,大叔让我摸一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:07.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我想给他们听一听雷夫先生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真正的战士啊 大叔果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.58,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我说的没错吧 托尔芬真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,等你长大后就来坐我的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,现在就让我坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.03,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是很奇怪啊 雷夫大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因为我爷爷说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:30.40,Vinland-pronunciation,,0,0,0,,{\pos(870,1000)}                Jörmungandr
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:30.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大海的西边有耶梦加得 会把靠近的船都吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:30.40,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,注：北欧神话中环绕人世的巨大海蛇，被奥丁扔进了无底深海之中。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然后再往西就什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:38.43,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,所以说啊 正是因为这样才衬托出我的伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.82,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你看 这个就是证据 证明我是真正的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,可是雷夫大叔你本来就不是战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.79,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你真是没搞明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是只有打仗的才叫做战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:53.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,水手要和大海战斗 这可不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.12,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大家都在说 大叔是长了胡子的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.20,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,就知道冒险 打仗的事情上一点都帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.84,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你们只会人云亦云
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔芬应该相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你觉得不去打仗只会冒险的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.43,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,所说的话都不可信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:25.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因为如果是说我爸爸是战士 那倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.23,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.98,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这些小鬼竟然瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你给我狠狠地说教下他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好了 今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,亚雷 送他们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好的 托尔兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:45.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,格陵兰那里有人冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,今年的寒流也会更强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大部分家畜应该都会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:16.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但真正的问题是气候正在逐年变冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.17,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.36,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有这两只变虚弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.07,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,很冷吧 尤尔瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,让叔叔给你暖一下身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,色老头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,妈妈 快睡吧 不然又要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,没事的 来帮我牵一下羊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.78,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,看来这里的情况也不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.41,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,说不定哪年冬天会冷到没人能熬过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:57.25,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,在我的国家那边 我的弟弟正在计划迁居
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,得迁很远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我可是往返一周回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,文兰就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔芬船长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.20,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,耶梦加得出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,放马过来吧 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐 去自己的床上睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.74,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,两个人太挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:43.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真狡猾 这张床是我先暖好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.79,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他们还在聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:55.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不用管他们 解决烦心事是大人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,别看他们了 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐给你抱一抱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,为什么我们家不买奴隶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.61,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,妈妈身体又不好 得要我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,别人家是别人家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.17,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要每年都问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,尤尔瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.74,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,还以为要摔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:38.87,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,没受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这下面…有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.51,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,尤尔瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,呐 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,昨天的故事有多少是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:20.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,全都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那么 让我坐坐这艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我亲眼见到的话就相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:28.68,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你这话的意思就是不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这么想坐船的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,坐你爸的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,看 那里还有艘军船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好像是村子里代代相传的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸会很乐意借给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父亲是个小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.81,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,拜托几次了都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是小气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔芬 这附近的海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我在年轻的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,被浮冰困住过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因为那时才移居到格陵兰不久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.51,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,所以大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,食物很快就吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.33,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只能靠吃冰来充饥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:15.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,最后船被冰川碾碎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:19.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们走投无路 只能在海上行走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,等我回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,就只剩下我一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.39,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,其他六个伙伴都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,为什么我们付出这么大代价
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,也要在这北方的岛上居住下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:46.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,赫尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,快煮热水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:49.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,尤尔瓦 拿兽皮来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.39,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.40,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这人埋在雪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,看着就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这怎么弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,让火烧旺些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,呐 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.59,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他已经死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,手脚都烂掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:21.99,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,而且这个人有点麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是这个村的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.97,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.94,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会在暴风雪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.21,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,还问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他是逃走的奴隶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,要是把他藏在这 会引发纠纷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们是逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:47.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们的先祖以前居住在更东的土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.26,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那片土地名叫挪威
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.07,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,比这里更温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,海也不会结冰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.82,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,有诸多海湾环绕的一块好土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.37,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,一个名为哈拉尔的强大男人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:09.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈拉尔的军队以燎原之势 镇压了各个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.63,Vinland-tips,,0,0,0,,注：哈拉尔一世（约850-933年），绰号“金发”哈拉尔，第一位挪威国王。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,他自诩为首次统一全挪威的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,成为了挪威的统治者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然后他逼迫所有人做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:23.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,服从国王 或者离开挪威这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,许多人厌恶哈拉尔的恶政
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.20,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,移居到了其统治范围之外的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:35.18,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那就是这里 冰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.33,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.97,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大叔果然是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.24,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父亲和我的祖先们怎么会逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,冒险老头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.42,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.10,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父亲 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,雷夫大叔说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.55,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,别处的奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.69,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,逃来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.23,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,活…活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.31,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你 能说名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.46,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.19,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,火 尤尔瓦 再烧旺些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:48.27,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我会被带回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.03,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,回到哈夫丹大人的宅邸里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:52.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.30,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,果然是从山的另一边过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.88,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我不要回去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:03.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:09.73,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我能去哪里…没有目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹到港口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那帮人又来找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有你能应付得来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那帮人说着什么奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,强行上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.16,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,虽然有雷夫先生在中间调解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,但年轻人都按捺不住想去干架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,反正快来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.39,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.39,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,是唯一适合人类的颈饰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,既不是金也不是银
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,是铁做的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:53.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,只有把锁链系在脖子上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:56.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,人类才有点利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.44,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不该这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:08.23,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,昨晚 我有一只奴隶挣断锁链逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.25,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你们有见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,别找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,反正就是为之前的事而来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.31,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,三番五次的 真是一群懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,和他们已经争执了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.65,Vinland-text - top,,0,0,0,,以为聚多点人我就会怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.80,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,前些天刚在居民大会上调停过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.64,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:29.69,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那次打架 我被你砍掉了左手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.35,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我也记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,竟然敢砍掉我大哥的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.44,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,住手 亚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.91,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大哥已经不能再走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.90,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我要把这混蛋的腿也给砍掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:42.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,法律和居民大会都吃屎去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈…哈夫丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.34,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,给你系上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.72,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,轻视法律者不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,法律即为锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,心术不正的家伙要被系上锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.89,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,才能开始成为一名人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.47,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不要忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.28,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,逃走的是个年轻的斯拉夫男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.18,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你们有见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:46.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我第一次体验到这么安稳的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.41,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,清醒过来 不然会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.38,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.50,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.63,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.69,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,大家都在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.80,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.45,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,因为大家都被卖到了不同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:15.84,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.99,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:26.10,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,在遥远的西方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:28.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,在海的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:31.65,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,有一块叫做「文兰」 的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:37.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那里气候温暖 物产丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:42.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,奴隶商人和战火也无法到达的远方土地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:44.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.09,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,将来与我们一起到那片土地去生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:54.58,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,文兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:22:59.48,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这里叫文兰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:20.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:22.58,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,原谅我的无礼 托尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:26.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我是那个奴隶正当的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.08,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.05,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父…父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:32.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,来这边 托尔芬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:34.57,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.41,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,不是藏起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.85,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你的奴隶快要死了 我们是在救他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:44.66,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.78,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,这个男人 多少钱买的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:51.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父…父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:54.15,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,问那种事情很不礼貌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:56.36,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,两头羊 年轻的母羊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.71,0:23:57.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我给你三头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:58.85,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:02.60,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怎样 哈夫丹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.04,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我要带那家伙回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.96,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,必须在其他奴隶面前拷打他 以儆效尤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.46,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那就四头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:20.86,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你这家伙 听不懂哈夫丹大人说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:22.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:25.99,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,如果我说加倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.41,0:24:28.33,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.70,0:24:30.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,全部都是三岁以下的母羊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.36,0:24:40.68,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,八头羊换个快死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:45.95,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,真是一单好买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.97,0:24:51.32,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,骗人吧 成交了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:56.14,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,托尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.45,0:24:59.51,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,你以为这就能解开那家伙的锁链吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.32,0:25:02.67,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,然后你能把他带到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.51,0:25:10.06,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,羊就让我们来挑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.64,0:25:27.49,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,姐姐 很伤心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.76,0:25:29.07,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,肯定伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.19,0:25:30.76,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,用八头羊换的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.87,0:25:32.31,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,马上就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.36,0:25:36.29,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父亲这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.57,0:25:38.92,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,怪家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:39.84,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.60,0:25:43.71,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们也是逃过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.46,0:25:45.75,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,雷夫大叔说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.59,0:25:49.70,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,我们的祖先是从东方逃过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.16,0:25:53.56,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,说是逃来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:57.54,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,没错 据说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.00,0:26:04.03,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.54,0:26:14.43,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,那么想从这里逃走的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.75,0:26:18.01,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,又能逃到哪里呢
